title: RPGitem权限问题
author: Yin_Wisdom
txt_content: RT 使用会出现An internal error occurred while attepting to perform this command 我是OP

replies.author: lichi2050
replies.txt_content:
* 首先你错版了，这个是插件，要到联机问答
* 然后出现An internal error occurred while attepting to perform this command 代表插件无效，你先检查一下你安装的插件版本和你服务器相应，如果不相应请去下载相应的。
